{"tid":2304471,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐正考慮完全退出美國零售銀行業務","createTime":"2020-11-28T22:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T08:15:26.000Z","uid":156363,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4a72e24911d2cb128b346a172e6a87a2e6d1ad05","tid":2304471,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:07:50.000Z","msg":"滙豐據報正考慮完全退出美國零售銀行業務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國金融時報引述消息人士報道，滙豐正尋求將資源從美國，轉移到盈利能力更強的亞洲業務，滙豐高級管理層打算在未來幾星期，向董事會提交計劃。<br />\n<br />\n但消息人士同時指出，滙豐未就美國零售業務的未來作出最終決定，正研究撤資成本的財務可行性，以及選擇完全退出，抑或保留較小業務，估計要明年才作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道說，如果關閉美國零售網絡，將會標誌著滙豐40年來，試圖在美經營提供全方位服務銀行的努力結束。"},{"pid":"a981aee5d76ffd1ec3c9e78d4ddc612a2dcf7023","tid":2304471,"uid":383914,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:12:20.000Z","msg":"做返真正的上海滙豐銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9b4ca596d2055326576a6c96f1bf76e037db2a","tid":2304471,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:13:18.000Z","msg":"佢不嬲業務重心都係亞洲"},{"pid":"f8eddf0feeb0c9d323abf3d7eb2330355cffcb6f","tid":2304471,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:14:32.000Z","msg":"柒婆有得開戶口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe26c401270f67fc765c4fdfd9f3c4d96324037a","tid":2304471,"uid":110719,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f8eddf0feeb0c9d323abf3d7eb2330355cffcb6f","tid":2304471,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:14:32.000Z","msg":"柒婆有得開戶口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:18:41.000Z","msg":"都係無 做得銀行都唔使旨意"},{"pid":"60ea21d8d0e8723a95032a2ccecf0dbff6fa88f3","tid":2304471,"uid":208376,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T22:23:36.000Z","msg":"零售銀行做平民生意咁low end不屌也罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse